    "original": " no longer has ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" no longer has \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "a0a4d5a0a49ec1f86c5178602a8c9170b39450f5963c5deb7da8a5d049c83ed6",
    "original": " now has ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" now has \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "aec4548804a16ff248041aa12c6930557ad2052469760b3762ba1add38511f60",
    "original": "Are you lot beast hunters? I've heard that some strange characters have shown up in %settlement% and are buying every exotic monster trophy they can find.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "c6926e7662d1341c494e01b0d53693f9036a3a3008a9bb4706e98a7417cb6c82",
    "original": "Collectors",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Collectors\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8636b5c036e906cdbe450cbec7cc3acdb4665e24d56ec198ef8ba052affd9a31",
    "original": "It seems all sorts of beast slayers and corpse-pickers are gathering in %settlement%. Something about selling beast trophies, I heard. Sounds like witchcraft to me.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "77839225ec36be5411ecf2baed46b3e4aa9c698607a5372e58439e43cde6724d",
    "original": "See this here dog tooth? I plan on selling it over in %settlement%, I heard they pay good coin for animal parts there.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "af49dc8b7d504c42d3c4dc578cb9b381eb622785039811a25faa7df4729a3316",
    "original": "Several collectors seeking exotic curios have made their way into town. There's good coin to be made selling beast trophies and like here.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"Several collectors seeking exotic curios have made their way into town. There's good coin to be made selling beast trophies and like here.\""
  }
]